  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >6 Minute Games</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/b0b9fce45d8a27950a2c5ff3270ce3ba.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=360 /></span><br>Almost instant respawns and constant action. A casual free game to play solo or with friends with short rounds—<i>and if you get bored just leave</i>—get into a match instantly & no waiting 30 minutes for a game to end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/d1739a0130f9e6a0bbeceafa4a36c06a.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=160 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/27223fb72b3dc8e1402e1ef31036c341.poster.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/27223fb72b3dc8e1402e1ef31036c341.webm?t=1723642330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/27223fb72b3dc8e1402e1ef31036c341.mp4?t=1723642330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Paint Warfare takes a refreshing turn away from other more tactical FPS games (and even some movement shooters). Equip a combo of 2 unique abilities to get a specific edge over your opponents<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/14470b22097a91448c89ab519e4a8948.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=160 /></span><br><br><strong>10 Abilities including:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Bullet shields<br></li><li>Dash<br></li><li>Jetpack<br></li><li>Grapple Hook<br></li><li>Invisibility<br></li><li>Turret, etc</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/f38c2554ba126e59c38f4cc38adbcc05.poster.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/f38c2554ba126e59c38f4cc38adbcc05.webm?t=1723642330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/f38c2554ba126e59c38f4cc38adbcc05.mp4?t=1723642330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Climb <i>any wall</i> you see holding the [space bar]<br></li><li>Fly across the map with the speed strips and boost ramps<br></li><li>Double jump<br></li><li>Slide or fall to the ground with [CTRL]</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/4c13dadfb588135726366f7f462537d5.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=160 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/dd93f2aed807475fbae3fca61e9aada2.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=160 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Maps:</strong> <br>13 unique maps to fight on.<br><br></li><li><strong>Game Modes:</strong> <br>6 gamemodes: <u>Minigame Free for all</u>, <u>Team Deathmatch</u>, <u>Capture the Flag</u>, <u>Hunger Games</u>, <u>Point Capture</u>, <u>Hunger Games</u> and private/ custom games!<br><br></li><li><strong>10 Abilities to unlock, such as:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Turret<br></li><li>Dash<br></li><li>Hang Glider<br></li><li>Invisibility<br></li><li>Grapple hook<br></li><li>Super speed boots<br></li><li>Heal<br></li><li>Jetpack<br></li><li>Enemy Radar<br></li><li>Half shield</li></ul><br></li><li><strong>Hats & gun skins:</strong><br>Collect coins through getting XP / completing challenges and unlock awesome skins for your rifles and character!<br><br></li><li> <strong>Guns:</strong> <br>Paint Warfare has (almost) everything, from <u>railguns</u> and <u>oranges</u> to <u>spoons</u>, <u>teleporters</u>, <u>gas guns</u> and <u>shotgun pistols</u>. I'm always adding suggestions! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/bba64f5c461a8e8103742bbfe7f36271.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=160 /></span><br>An awesome free game to play with friends! It's easy to join your friend's lobby using the match codes, or you can create your own private game with your own game rules!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/9c94a991c2864d73efec95d958ab64b9.poster.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/9c94a991c2864d73efec95d958ab64b9.webm?t=1723642330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/9c94a991c2864d73efec95d958ab64b9.mp4?t=1723642330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
