ns through getting XP / completing challenges and unlock awesome skins for your rifles and character!<br><br></li><li> <strong>Guns:</strong> <br>Paint Warfare has (almost) everything, from <u>railguns</u> and <u>oranges</u> to <u>spoons</u>, <u>teleporters</u>, <u>gas guns</u> and <u>shotgun pistols</u>. I'm always adding suggestions! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/bba64f5c461a8e8103742bbfe7f36271.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=160 /></span><br>An awesome free game to play with friends! It's easy to join your friend's lobby using the match codes, or you can create your own private game with your own game rules!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/9c94a991c2864d73efec95d958ab64b9.poster.avif?t=1723642330\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/9c94a991c2864d73efec95d958ab64b9.webm?t=1723642330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1190150/extras/9c94a991c2864d73efec95d958ab64b9.mp4?t=1723642330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
